name: Login Test Feature
description:
In Order to perform successful Login
  As a Admin
  I should verify different scenarios for login

children.name: User should login successfully
Given I am on login page
When I login to the application
And I navigate to the Home page
Then I get a message "Dashboard"
User should see the logo on homepage successfully
Given I am on login page
When I login to the application
And I navigate to the Home page
Then I should see the logo
User should logout successfully
Given I am on login page
When I login to the application
And I navigate to the Home page
And I click on user profile logo
And I click on log out button
And I logout successfully
Then I should get a text "Login Panel"
